div.div:
The three entity classes involved in a many-to-many relationship, using
a linking table. This type of many-to-many relationship is used only if you have extra
data in the linking table entity class. In this case, the BookAuthor class contains
an Order property that defines the order in which the Author Names should be
displayed alongside a Book.
